            "class": "joshie.enchiridion.books.features.FeatureText",
            "properties": {
              "text": "Last but not least simply press the delete key to remove a feature from the page.\r\nNow that we have got the basics of moving, resizing, copying and deleting items, let\u0027s take a moment to talk about the top right.\r\n\r\nFrom right to left. \r\n[b]Cross:[/b] Deletes the Page\r\n[b]Square:[/b] Change the background of the book\r\n[b]Book:[/b] Change the icon of the book\r\n[i]If you have reload resources off this will require a restart to work[/i]\r\n[b]Grid:[/b] Toggles various grids which allow you to snap features when moving them, making it easier to align various things.",
              "size": 1.0
            }
          },
          "isLocked": false,
          "isHidden": false,
          "layerIndex": 2
